origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
[['LeaseFinanceSearch.find_companies', {'name': 'LeaseFinanceSearch.find_companies', 'description': 'This function searches for lease finance companies based on location.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location where the lease finance companies operate.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'companies', 'description': 'A list of up to three lease finance companies, each with an ID, name, and location.'}]}], ['LeaseFinanceSearch.get_company_details', {'name': 'LeaseFinanceSearch.get_company_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed information about a specific lease finance company given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'companyId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the lease finance company.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'details', 'description': 'Detailed information about the company, including business scope, advantages, and contact information.'}]}], ['LeaseFinanceSearch.compare_companies', {'name': 'LeaseFinanceSearch.compare_companies', 'description': 'This function compares multiple lease finance companies based on their IDs.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'companyIds', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of company IDs to compare.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'comparison', 'description': 'A comparison of the selected companies, highlighting differences in services, advantages, and market presence.'}]}], ['LeaseFinanceRiskAnalysis.analyze_risks_and_benefits', {'name': 'LeaseFinanceRiskAnalysis.analyze_risks_and_benefits', 'description': 'This function analyzes the risks and benefits of lease finance for a given set of companies.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'companyIds', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of company IDs to analyze.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'analysis', 'description': 'An analysis of the risks and benefits associated with lease finance for the selected companies.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `LeaseFinanceSearch.find_companies` 并传入 `location`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "LeaseFinanceSearch.find_companies",
    "args": "{'location': 'China'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
